mention.text: the future deputies and senators of democracy and progress

the millions of chilean men and women who in sunshine or rain throughout chile filled up stadiums , plazas , and streets , chanting out slogans for the future ; to those who saw the street with the symbol of the star of hope ; to those who pasted my picture on walls , windows , and notebooks ; to those who encouraged me in this tiresome but moving campaign with an embrace , a handshake , or a smile ; to all those
